SELECT cn.name AS company_name FROM company_name AS cn, movie_companies AS mc WHERE cn.country_code ='[sm]' AND cn.name LIKE '%Film%' AND cn.id = mc.company_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM info_type AS it, movie_info AS mi WHERE it.info = 'bottom 10 rank' AND it.id = mi.info_type_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM movie_info AS mi, title AS t WHERE t.production_year > 2004 AND t.id = mi.movie_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM movie_info AS mi, title AS t WHERE t.production_year < 2011 AND t.id = mi.movie_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM movie_info AS mi, title AS t WHERE mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'USA', 'German') AND t.id = mi.movie_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk WHERE mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'USA', 'German') AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM movie_info AS mi, movie_link AS ml WHERE mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'USA', 'German') AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM movie_info AS mi, complete_cast AS cc WHERE mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'USA', 'German') AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM info_type AS it, movie_info AS mi WHERE it.info ='rating' AND it.id = mi.info_type_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM info_type AS it, movie_info AS mi WHERE it.info ='mini biography' AND it.id = mi.info_type_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM info_type AS it, movie_info AS mi WHERE it.info = 'top 250 rank' AND it.info = 'bottom 10 rank' AND it.id = mi.info_type_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM info_type AS it, movie_info AS mi WHERE it.info = 'top 250 rank' AND it.info = 'bottom 10 rank' AND it.id = mi.info_type_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM info_type AS it, movie_info AS mi WHERE it.info = 'bottom 10 rank' AND it.info ='rating' AND it.id = mi.info_type_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM movie_info AS mi, movie_companies AS mc WHERE mc.note NOT LIKE '%(as Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer Pictures)%' AND mc.note IS NULL AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM movie_info AS mi, movie_companies AS mc WHERE mc.note LIKE '%(presents)%' AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'USA', 'German') AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM movie_info AS mi, title AS t WHERE t.production_year < 2011 AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'USA', 'German') AND t.id = mi.movie_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM movie_info AS mi, info_type AS it WHERE mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'USA', 'German') AND it.info ='mini biography' AND it.id = mi.info_type_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM info_type AS it, movie_info AS mi WHERE it.info ='rating' AND it.info ='mini biography' AND it.id = mi.info_type_id;
SELECT mi.info AS release_date FROM movie_info AS mi, movie_companies AS mc WHERE mc.note LIKE '%(France)%' AND mc.note IS NOT NULL AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id;

SELECT at.title AS aka_title FROM movie_companies AS mc, aka_title AS at WHERE mc.note NOT LIKE '%(as Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer Pictures)%' AND mc.note IS NULL AND mc.movie_id = at.movie_id;
